Homemade little creation (bit off topic) : A STRAWBERRY PIE üçìüç∞ ! üòª

We publish a lot of sometime complex recipe, today we've made something simple and seasonal. Hope you'll like it, recipe bellow ---- ü•ß For the shortcrust pastry: 250 g of flour, 125 g of caster sugar, 1 egg, 100 g of butter, 1 lemon zest, 1 pinch of salt  In a bowl, mix the egg with powdered sugar and a pinch of salt.  Put the flour on the worktop, make a well in the center, pour the contents of the bowl and the lemon zest, then the melted butter (especially not liquid butter!). Mix everything until you get a homogeneous paste. Roll it out.  Bake in a hot oven for 12 to 15 minutes. Possibility to put aluminum foil on it, to be sure it doesn't burn. üç∞ Mix the mascarpone with 80g of sugar and 1 and a half sachets of vanilla sugar, add the strawberries cut in half, set aside in the fridge and serve fresh.  #foodphotography #piercings #strawberry #foodie #strawberrycheesecake #strawberrys #instafoods #pie #prilaga #strawberryblonde #foodgasm #instafood #pier #instafoodapp #piercing #foodporn #food #foodstagram #strawberryshortcake #instafoodies #instafoodie #pies #pierced #strawberrycake
